%h3 Payment Methods

- @payment_methods.each do |payment_method|
  .col-md-12
    %span.col-md-11.label-font
      = link_to payment_method.name.titleize, edit_payment_method_path(current_user.id, payment_method.id)
    %span.col-md-1
      = link_to fa_icon("trash-o", class: "fa-2x"), payment_method_path(current_user, payment_method.id), method: :delete, data: {confirm: "Are you sure?"}
